title: Ep. 160 - Republicans Fail To Defund Planned Parenthood
description:
Justice Kavanaugh took sides with the liberal justices on the court to protect Planned Parenthood funding. Meanwhile, Republicans have completed a two year stint with complete control over the legislative branch and Planned Parenthood funding remains intact. There is no “pro-life party” in America. 12-11-2018
